title.native: プリキュアオールスターズDX みんなともだちっ☆奇跡の全員大集合!
title.romaji: Precure All Stars DX: Minna Tomodachi☆Kiseki no Zenin Daishuugou!

description: Love, Miki and Inori are on their way to a dance contest, but get lost on their way to Minato Mirai. Still looking for their way, they are attacked by a monster. When the three Fresh Precure girls start to fight it, other Precures show up to support them. They all have to combine their powers to win against this mighty enemy.
synonyms: Eiga Precure All Stars DX: Minna Tomodachi - Kiseki no Zenin Daishuugou!

[Wiki (jp)](https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/東堂いづみ) | [Wiki (en)](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Izumi_Todo)

Izumi Toudou is a collective pseudonym for [Toei Animation](https://anilist.co/studio/18/)'s staff.

Mayu Kudou is a Japanese singer. Since performing the opening theme of [Yes! Precure 5](https://anilist.co/anime/1932), she has been a prominent voice in the Precure franchise. She was in Jazz Vocal Unit called Harajuku BJ Girls (Chix Chicks) in 2005-2010.

[Twitter](https://twitter.com/suzumevachi)

Freelancer formerly affiliated with [Toei Animation](https://anilist.co/studio/18/).

Close friends with [Rie Matsumoto](https://anilist.co/staff/107664/), and the two often work together.

[Wiki (jp)](https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/行信三)

Affiliated with [Toei Animation](https://anilist.co/studio/18/) since the early '80s.

Married to [Yukie Yuki](https://anilist.co/staff/135806/).

[Twitter](https://twitter.com/naokisato_face) | [Spotify](https://open.spotify.com/artist/1hlpldRj6GZ2naD4XDqi80)

Naoki Sato is a Japanese composer and producer who has provided the music for several popular anime series. He was born on May 2, 1970 and graduated in Chiba Prefecture and Tokyo College of Music. At the 29th Japanese Academy Awards in 2006, he won the Best Music prize for his work on the film Always Sanchōme no Yuhi.
Mizuno Sayaka is a music selector working for Swara Production
**Masayuki Nishide** is a Japanese producer and animation planner, who works for the Asahi Broadcasting Corporation (ABC).

[Twitter](https://twitter.com/waka_fuumi)

A regular presence in the [Precure](https://anilist.co/anime/603/) franchise since its beginning.
**Kazuhiro Asao** is a Japanese producer and animation planner.
